        <title type="html"><![CDATA[Doomfist's Identity]]></title>
        <id>https://WakeTechBrandon.github.io/tech-portfolio/blog/2022/12/5/Overwatch-2-Gameplay-Hero-Doomfist-Philosophy.html</id>
        <link href="https://WakeTechBrandon.github.io/tech-portfolio/blog/2022/12/5/Overwatch-2-Gameplay-Hero-Doomfist-Philosophy.html"/>
